                        <interp inst="t18361024-2318-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 19.—
<rs id="t18361024-2318-punishment-65" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18361024-2318-punishment-65" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2318-18361024 t18361024-2318-punishment-65"></join>Transported for Fourteen Years</rs>.</p>
